name: 3rd International Conference on Food and Nutrition
content: USFN is immensely privileged and excited to extend an invitation to all practitioners, researchers, experimenters, scholars, experts, professionals, officials, and others, from nations throughout the globe, who are operating in the Food and Beverage industries to participate in 3rd ICFN 2020, scheduled to be held on the 20th and 21st of November 2020, in the breath takingly glorious city of Malaysia.
